<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The primitive relation that express the concept of an entity being part of another one."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "OWL2 does not allow non-simple (e.g. transitive) properties to appear in disjoint property axioms. We therefore implement the transitivity of hasPart using SWRL rules instead of asserting it with owl:TransitiveProperty."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between a process and an object participating to it, i.e. that is relevant to the process itself."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasParticipant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "Participation is a parthood relation: you must be part of the process to contribute to it. A participant whose 4D extension is totally contained within the process."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pink#Method> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#Process> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a method to the process that it describes."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasProcess"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The starting point for this relation is that it relates a method to an activity it describes. However, when an activity is described by a method is a process. Therefor is the range of this relation a process and not only an activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "This is a subproperty of participatesTo, meaning that the process is overcrossed by the method."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A semiotic relation that connects a semiotic object to a property in a declaration process."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasProperty"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A proper part of a whole, whose parts always cover the full temporal extension of the whole within a spatial interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasSpatialPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The part is connected with the rest item or members with hasContact relations only (no hasNext)."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A relation that identify a proper item part of the whole, whose parts always cover the full spatial extension of the whole within a time interval." .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasTemporalPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "A temporal part of an item cannot both cause and be caused by any other proper part of the item."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#input
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#attributed> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pink#Method> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a method to an entity via a process that used the entity and that the method participates to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "input"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#input> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The process P is through overlapped by the agent A and overcrossed by the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E causes P."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#causedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A one-directional relation between an entity that affects the subject."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "isAfter"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy
<https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between an entity that overlaps another without having it as part."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "isOvercrossedBy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#method
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#Method> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a dataset to the method that describes the activity it was created with." .
<https://w3id.org/pink#method> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "method"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between two individuals that does not share any parts."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "nonOverlaps"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#output
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#attributed> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pink#Method> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a method to an entity via a process that was generated by the entity and that the method participates to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "output"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The process P is through overlapped by the agent A and overcrossed by the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E is caused by P."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between two individuals representing entities that share at least one of their parts."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "overlaps"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relation an entity to an activity that it interacts with."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "participatesTo"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The entity through overlaps the activity."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Indirect relation that relates the output of an activity to its input."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "processedFrom"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#SsbdDimension> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "One of `pink:functionality`, `pink:safety`, `pink:environmental_sustainability`, `pink:social_sustainability`"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Note this class redefined in PR https://github.com/PINK-project/PINK-annotation-schema/pull/15"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ssbdDimension"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#used
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#used> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an entity that it used."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "For example, :baking :used :spoon, :egg, :oven ." .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "used"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E causes A."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAssociatedWith> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an agent that had some (unspecified) responsibility for the occurence of this activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasAssociatedWith"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The activity is through overlapped by the agent."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAttributedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#causedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an entity to an agent via an activity that both the entity and agent participates to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasAttributedTo"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The activity is through overlapped by the agent and overcrossed by the entity."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy
