<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Indirect relation that relates the output entity of an activity to its input entity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasDerivedBy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasGeneratedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an entity to the activity it was generated from."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasGeneratedBy"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#skopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E is caused by A."@en .
