<https://w3id.org/pink#Model> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A useful simplified description of a selected part of the world."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Model> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Newton's law of motion is a model for how a body will move when subjected to forces.\nA mouse can be seen as a model for a human (e.g. in medicine).\nAn architectural floor plan is a model of a house.\n"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Model> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Model"@en .
