# https://w3id.org/pink#Role
<https://w3id.org/pink#Role> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Role> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "An individual can be said to have a role in relation to the entity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Role> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The class of all individuals that are defined through a parthood relation to an entity."@en .
